item.title: DASH
item.description: score:9 Chances: DoorDash (DASH) reported fourth-quarter revenue of $2.30 billion topping estimates of $2.24 billion. Adjusted EBITDA of $363 million was better than the expected $356.2 million. The first quarter and full-year outlooks were about in line with expectations. Risks: DoorDash continues to struggle to return to pre-pandemic levels of growth.
